    <h1>To the President of Congress, No. 86</h1>
    
    <div class="docbody">
     <div class="opener">
      <table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationLeft">Sir</td>
		<td class="salutationRight">Paris June 17 1780</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
     </div>
     <p>The Writer on the Consequences of American Independence, Subjoins a Comparison between the United States, and the West Indies.</p>
     <p>He says the Exports from England was in 1771<a class="ptr" href="#PJA09d304n1" id="PJA09d304n1-ptr">1</a></p>
